[
  {
    "text": "Climbing the corporate ladder, building a huge successful business, investing and getting returns like Warren Buffett, why do we actually do it?",
    "uid": "384cb83498aee592",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 0.27,
    "end": 9.27
  },
  {
    "text": "Answer, money, more money.",
    "uid": "f5c9aacbb74fffd8",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 10.27,
    "end": 14.27
  },
  {
    "text": "But let's take a step back.",
    "uid": "af1fdd20df2bc1ec",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 14.27,
    "end": 17.27
  },
  {
    "text": "What does money create?",
    "uid": "93eaaa03734c61d5",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 17.27,
    "end": 19.27
  },
  {
    "text": "It creates time, mobility and options.",
    "uid": "946b3bd6744770dd",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 19.27,
    "end": 23.27
  },
  {
    "text": "The new rich is a group of people who have realized that living like a millionaire doesn't require that one is a millionaire.",
    "uid": "6ec5425f5757e23f",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 24.27,
    "end": 31.27
  },
  {
    "text": "They've also realized that you can live like a millionaire without working your ass off until age 65, building a Fortune 500 company, or consuming millions of annual reports.",
    "uid": "7e7aba976cc94cc4",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 32.27,
    "end": 42.27
  },
  {
    "text": "In the four-hour workweek, a book written by the entrepreneur Team Ferris,",
    "uid": "359122b770fcb00e",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 44.27,
    "end": 48.27
  },
  {
    "text": "we shall learn how the new rich managed to do this.",
    "uid": "d2183d011f2d44fd",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 48.27,
    "end": 51.27
  },
  {
    "text": "At the end of this video, you'll be able to fill in these blanks.",
    "uid": "c68552f61430a55a",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 52.27,
    "end": 55.27
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's dive in.",
    "uid": "7744fa6b986e2016",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 58.0,
    "end": 59.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Take away number one, the step-by-step process of joining the new rich.",
    "uid": "5b7fb6d19be99ded",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 63.26,
    "end": 67.26
  },
  {
    "text": "Create time, mobility and options without having any abundance of money.",
    "uid": "a17112cf25eeac46",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 69.26,
    "end": 73.26
  },
  {
    "text": "Sounds like a great deal. Am I right?",
    "uid": "6458a8589b298a98",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 73.26,
    "end": 75.26
  },
  {
    "text": "That's why the strategy to get there is abbreviated D-E-A-L,",
    "uid": "43d79fb378eae995",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 76.26,
    "end": 80.26
  },
  {
    "text": "Life is negotiable.",
    "uid": "0f02d11ea7c30358",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 82.26,
    "end": 84.26
  },
  {
    "text": "Just because everyone else follows the 95 dogma doesn't mean that you have to do it too.",
    "uid": "ce184b9b5e3979de",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 85.26,
    "end": 90.26
  },
  {
    "text": "I hate the, but what if everyone else does so too, argument?",
    "uid": "8eaaba7fdda3e6b7",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 91.26,
    "end": 96.26
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't worry, everyone won't be willing to do this, but hopefully you will.",
    "uid": "261c4f34c4e0a976",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 97.26,
    "end": 102.26
  },
  {
    "text": "Follow this and you'll be ready to join the new rich in no time.",
    "uid": "82f4dea85d940a5e",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 103.26,
    "end": 106.26
  },
  {
    "text": "D stands for definition.",
    "uid": "b3fd9695229d32bf",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 107.26,
    "end": 109.26
  },
  {
    "text": "First and foremost, we must redefine the goal of the game that we've been fooled play for so long.",
    "uid": "880bb1190ca3a793",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 110.26,
    "end": 116.26
  },
  {
    "text": "Money in itself is not the end goal.",
    "uid": "08bb3e94b3d25efe",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 117.26,
    "end": 120.26
  },
  {
    "text": "Relative income trumps absolute income, one certain essentials are met, more on this in techway number two.",
    "uid": "68dbb936064c5bc2",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 121.26,
    "end": 127.26
  },
  {
    "text": "E is for elimination.",
    "uid": "0a6878095d7da445",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 129.54,
    "end": 131.54
  },
  {
    "text": "Being busy 24-7 is trumped as ambitious, but Team Ferris disagrees.",
    "uid": "2e98273250882006",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 132.54,
    "end": 137.54
  },
  {
    "text": "Being busy all the time is lazy, lazy thinking.",
    "uid": "3c03cad0dfd5df2b",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 137.54,
    "end": 142.54
  },
  {
    "text": "To become truly productive, which is essential to have a four hour work week,",
    "uid": "e61f04abb771d967",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 143.54,
    "end": 147.54
  },
  {
    "text": "you must eliminate unimportant activities, which we'll discuss in techway number three.",
    "uid": "68cd55b1128c9063",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 148.54,
    "end": 152.54
  },
  {
    "text": "A is for automation.",
    "uid": "c78f0b67db42d91d",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 155.02,
    "end": 157.02
  },
  {
    "text": "Outsource, outsource, outsource.",
    "uid": "661ee4cf62cac7a0",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 158.02,
    "end": 160.02
  },
  {
    "text": "No more wasting your time with repetitive tasks.",
    "uid": "c86eb11733725884",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 161.02,
    "end": 164.02
  },
  {
    "text": "If you estimate your hourly to be, say, $20, it probably makes a lot of sense to have someone else do it for $7 an hour.",
    "uid": "4581f240d1b94ae0",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 164.02,
    "end": 171.02
  },
  {
    "text": "More on this in techway number four.",
    "uid": "b05d6713beb7b8f7",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 172.02,
    "end": 174.02
  },
  {
    "text": "L is for liberation.",
    "uid": "1127e7262b88794e",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 175.02,
    "end": 178.02
  },
  {
    "text": "Skin is better in Italy.",
    "uid": "df4af15e77adfeab",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 179.02,
    "end": 181.02
  },
  {
    "text": "Surfing is better in Costa Rica, diving is better in Australia, and meatballs definitely taste better in Sweden.",
    "uid": "7b3fec7132136416",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 182.02,
    "end": 188.02
  },
  {
    "text": "Why tie yourself down to a single location?",
    "uid": "f273d52600cfcad8",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 189.02,
    "end": 191.02
  },
  {
    "text": "In techway number five, I'll discuss some of the tips that Team Ferris gives for the final piece of the puzzle, mobility.",
    "uid": "13bcbed6409bcf58",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 192.02,
    "end": 198.02
  },
  {
    "text": "Takeway number two.",
    "uid": "9567161389d62365",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 203.5,
    "end": 204.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Relative income, trumps absolute income.",
    "uid": "7436d26d80b41444",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 205.5,
    "end": 207.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Okay, so D is for definition, and it's all about redefining how we think about money.",
    "uid": "22c52db8c50de6ca",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 209.5,
    "end": 215.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Who is richer in your opinion?",
    "uid": "f567e1fe11c9e369",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 216.5,
    "end": 218.5
  },
  {
    "text": "A. The investment banker with an annual salary of $500,000, who works 80 hours a week, or B.",
    "uid": "dfec0814094d1436",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 219.5,
    "end": 227.5
  },
  {
    "text": "The e-commerce entrepreneur with his whole business on autopilot, who earns $40,000 per year with a four hour work week.",
    "uid": "dbe2c1557ecf7e5d",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 228.5,
    "end": 235.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Team Ferris talks about something he calls a freedom multiplier, consisting of four variables.",
    "uid": "a9ed67a7a3d72dd0",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 237.5,
    "end": 242.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Depending on how many of them that you can control, the practical value of your money multiplies.",
    "uid": "f048ef831329046c",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 243.5,
    "end": 249.5
  },
  {
    "text": "They are, what you do, when you do it, where you do it, and whom you do it with.",
    "uid": "14a092fc645e3b7d",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 250.5,
    "end": 257.5
  },
  {
    "text": "An investment banker is typically very restricted in these regards, which is why the e-commerce entrepreneur may be richer when we consider what money can do for this person.",
    "uid": "0c05543b24a0ce8f",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 258.5,
    "end": 268.5
  },
  {
    "text": "And here, we shall introduce a very important concept, relative income, trumps absolute income.",
    "uid": "459c39c8bb445dc0",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 269.5,
    "end": 275.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Once you have a cash flow, that's enough to support your desired lifestyle.",
    "uid": "b38e308f70257191",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 276.5,
    "end": 280.5
  },
  {
    "text": "By the way, for great inspiration on a millionaire lifestyle, check out my summary of Dan Lok's F.U. Money.",
    "uid": "07bd2b54f0e88f44",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 281.5,
    "end": 286.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Sure, the investment banker beats the e-commerce entrepreneur in absolute income.",
    "uid": "43b3479d62e826b8",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 287.5,
    "end": 292.5
  },
  {
    "text": "He earns $460,000 more per year.",
    "uid": "81d91683bb521549",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 292.5,
    "end": 296.5
  },
  {
    "text": "But is this a bit excessive?",
    "uid": "f8e89f79fa0e80e4",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 297.5,
    "end": 299.5
  },
  {
    "text": "The e-commerce entrepreneur beats the investment banker once time is introduced to the equation, as his relative income is $200 per hour, versus $120 for the banker.",
    "uid": "11624f1668b196cb",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 300.5,
    "end": 311.5
  },
  {
    "text": "The investment banker may be able to stack up that $500,000 salary for an early retirement,",
    "uid": "970d6369e6bec7bc",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 313.5,
    "end": 318.5
  },
  {
    "text": "but he should question himself on why he wants to do so, so that he can move to a nice and warm paradise island and just go surfing all day.",
    "uid": "33b50638d3b0ee80",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 318.5,
    "end": 328.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, the e-commerce entrepreneur can live that lifestyle already. He doesn't have to wait until retirement to do so, and this every reason, not to save it all till the end.",
    "uid": "c5051cc5ec023b52",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 331.86,
    "end": 343.86
  },
  {
    "text": "Take away number three, how to be more productive.",
    "uid": "baae72a2396b6627",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 343.86,
    "end": 355.22
  },
  {
    "text": "What's the difference between being effective and being efficient?",
    "uid": "bd15b8860f1234a9",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 356.22,
    "end": 360.22
  },
  {
    "text": "Being effective is about doing the right things.",
    "uid": "da374c8413487fa9",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 361.22,
    "end": 364.22
  },
  {
    "text": "Being efficient is about doing things right.",
    "uid": "c35d78d00e780fbc",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 365.22,
    "end": 367.22
  },
  {
    "text": "To join the new rich and reach a four hour work week, we must focus on the former.",
    "uid": "f52ed0321c3be17f",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 368.22,
    "end": 373.22
  },
  {
    "text": "Remember this, doing something unimportant well does not make it important.",
    "uid": "75773bbbe721336d",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 374.22,
    "end": 379.22
  },
  {
    "text": "It's time to eliminate the activities that are not getting us where we want.",
    "uid": "fabc925c0aa66c2c",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 379.22,
    "end": 384.22
  },
  {
    "text": "There are two great principles to keep in mind here.",
    "uid": "6d9d2909c6a5c7a2",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 386.22,
    "end": 389.22
  },
  {
    "text": "Paratos law and Parkinson's law.",
    "uid": "846646e3f0810a3a",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 390.22,
    "end": 392.22
  },
  {
    "text": "Paratos law states that 80% of the effects comes from 20% of the causes.",
    "uid": "a5ab9e4df63726e3",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 394.76,
    "end": 398.76
  },
  {
    "text": "80% of company profits comes from 20% of the customers.",
    "uid": "11bba1cea8dae695",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 399.76,
    "end": 403.76
  },
  {
    "text": "80% of results comes from 20% of effort and time.",
    "uid": "f138f24425c5e073",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 404.76,
    "end": 407.76
  },
  {
    "text": "80% of consequences stems from 20% of the problems, etc.",
    "uid": "0aec89eb35c950f3",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 407.76,
    "end": 412.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Our mental energy must focus on these 20%.",
    "uid": "57ebddf060451cbd",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 413.76,
    "end": 417.76
  },
  {
    "text": "For example, keep the top 20% customers happy and put the remaining 80% on autopilot.",
    "uid": "1bbfbf81418e0402",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 418.76,
    "end": 424.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Fire their asses if they complain.",
    "uid": "4020005740472ba1",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 425.76,
    "end": 427.76
  },
  {
    "text": "In general, keep updating priorities and focus each day on one to two big tasks.",
    "uid": "c16eb7e803192231",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 428.76,
    "end": 434.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Small bad things will happen when you start to ignore certain tasks, but this is necessary to get the big things done.",
    "uid": "5303ec8837220740",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 435.76,
    "end": 442.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Parkinson's law states that a task will grow in perceived importance and complexity in proportion to how much time that is allowed for its completion.",
    "uid": "91fa89526b1ca841",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 444.76,
    "end": 453.76
  },
  {
    "text": "I've got to become better at this myself.",
    "uid": "56c39a498f0dac3c",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 454.76,
    "end": 457.76
  },
  {
    "text": "I've had days when I've built a whole website in one day, but I've also had days when I searched for a flight tickets for a whole day, without even booking one.",
    "uid": "0ef0baeb27e27fee",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 458.76,
    "end": 466.76
  },
  {
    "text": "It's all about deadlines.",
    "uid": "7c8c109f7ff17d43",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 467.76,
    "end": 469.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Do you become as productive as possible cultivate the habit of setting short ones both for yourself and for others?",
    "uid": "da393040c4bcf986",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 470.76,
    "end": 477.76
  },
  {
    "text": "24 to 72 hours is preferred and if the task seems to be too big for that, junk it down.",
    "uid": "4613a9de08bdfa8e",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 478.76,
    "end": 484.76
  },
  {
    "text": "This is closely related to the students syndrome, by the way.",
    "uid": "7233f4be859293a5",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 485.76,
    "end": 488.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Smash the like button if you've experienced this, partly so that I don't feel alone, but mostly for the YouTube algorithm.",
    "uid": "3977056f6b6a11a5",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 489.76,
    "end": 495.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Take away number four, become the ghost in the machine.",
    "uid": "d2e64636487cae66",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 496.76,
    "end": 504.02
  },
  {
    "text": "What's the greatest obstacle towards management free money?",
    "uid": "19b05850c21ecc14",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 506.02,
    "end": 509.02
  },
  {
    "text": "No matter if you're an employee or an entrepreneur,",
    "uid": "697a6ac7af5dd4a9",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 513.02,
    "end": 516.02
  },
  {
    "text": "to join the new rich, you must learn how to define and delegate tasks.",
    "uid": "e857eb9c32cc8289",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 516.02,
    "end": 521.02
  },
  {
    "text": "Replace and multiply yourself.",
    "uid": "5d377199fa514ffd",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 522.02,
    "end": 524.02
  },
  {
    "text": "Out-source tasks either to machines and software or to people to have them automated from your perspective.",
    "uid": "5fdcb0b02600add6",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 525.02,
    "end": 531.02
  },
  {
    "text": "Illumination precedes automation, because just like doing something unimportant well does not make it important,",
    "uid": "fdea1101a695a9c4",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 532.02,
    "end": 539.02
  },
  {
    "text": "outsourcing something unimportant does not make it important either.",
    "uid": "12ce890db8c6fce3",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 540.02,
    "end": 543.02
  },
  {
    "text": "But they also go somewhat hand in hand.",
    "uid": "6f65f9ccfe18386b",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 543.02,
    "end": 547.02
  },
  {
    "text": "By paying someone else to do an activity for you, you can quickly determine if it's something that should be done or not.",
    "uid": "c9036d0a6b766a3a",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 548.02,
    "end": 554.02
  },
  {
    "text": "Would you pay someone $7 an hour to manage customers that you only profit $5 an hour from?",
    "uid": "fbfcc8cbe3bb931e",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 555.02,
    "end": 560.02
  },
  {
    "text": "Of course not.",
    "uid": "49ec64656cd41d91",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 561.02,
    "end": 562.02
  },
  {
    "text": "And it's even crazy for you to handle these customers yourself, as you probably value your own time, much more than $7 an hour.",
    "uid": "12918b8de590837f",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 563.02,
    "end": 570.02
  },
  {
    "text": "These customers should be eliminated, not outsourced.",
    "uid": "cf27bcab4a2b3d8e",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 570.02,
    "end": 574.02
  },
  {
    "text": "Tim Ferriss talks about geographic arbitrauching.",
    "uid": "64b9749f7c57a334",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 575.02,
    "end": 579.36
  },
  {
    "text": "It's all about earning in dollars, living on pesos and compensating in rupees.",
    "uid": "ffe060e5d0e631f6",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 580.36,
    "end": 585.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Get a virtual assistant from, for instance, Fiver or Upwork for time-consuming and repetitive tasks and remember the following.",
    "uid": "37d27c435004bd25",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 586.36,
    "end": 593.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Focus on cost per task completed and not cost per hour.",
    "uid": "dd153e703d99d2ed",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 594.36,
    "end": 598.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Test. You don't know how well you will work with anyone before you try it.",
    "uid": "093e0759c83a4c09",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 598.36,
    "end": 603.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Set short deadlines.",
    "uid": "744ec3f542965add",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 604.36,
    "end": 607.36
  },
  {
    "text": "One task at a time.",
    "uid": "5c6c11ca88bc50b0",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 608.36,
    "end": 610.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Apply it. Try it.",
    "uid": "260810cecc7629e6",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 611.36,
    "end": 613.36
  },
  {
    "text": "And hopefully you can multiply yourself down the line, making you the ghost in the machinery.",
    "uid": "ed889857095e3171",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 614.36,
    "end": 618.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Take away number five. Create unrestricted mobility.",
    "uid": "a73edad4b22e550d",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 619.36,
    "end": 625.37
  },
  {
    "text": "Yes, even as an employee.",
    "uid": "97118812c15b2121",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 626.37,
    "end": 628.37
  },
  {
    "text": "For the entrepreneur, unrestricted mobility follows from eliminating and automating.",
    "uid": "62a15e53018ae204",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 628.37,
    "end": 634.37
  },
  {
    "text": "If you start with the right business.",
    "uid": "da3288d3e338b6b6",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 635.37,
    "end": 637.37
  },
  {
    "text": "An example of such a business is an internet-based one.",
    "uid": "7bc9c94033225e55",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 638.37,
    "end": 641.37
  },
  {
    "text": "And I'll have to tune my own horn again and recommend my summary of a few money, where I discuss the seven golden rules to internet riches.",
    "uid": "f174f69507de090c",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 642.37,
    "end": 649.37
  },
  {
    "text": "For the employee, however, it's a bit different.",
    "uid": "321d90021b8b6afa",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 650.37,
    "end": 654.37
  },
  {
    "text": "You can't just tell the boss that from now on, he'll be working from the beaches in Rio de Janeiro.",
    "uid": "2aac344840f58073",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 654.37,
    "end": 660.37
  },
  {
    "text": "No. Instead, you should follow these five steps to gradually allow yourself to pull a disappearing act from the office.",
    "uid": "7b9ff3e0d4afcf18",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 661.37,
    "end": 669.37
  },
  {
    "text": "Step one. Increase investment.",
    "uid": "578887a1bf3441a6",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 670.37,
    "end": 674.37
  },
  {
    "text": "Look for courses and additional training available for employees.",
    "uid": "5636ee1c78fbb7d1",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 675.37,
    "end": 678.37
  },
  {
    "text": "You want the company to invest as much as possible in you because no one understands sun costs.",
    "uid": "e9e4b5f5a5dd3c01",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 678.37,
    "end": 684.37
  },
  {
    "text": "Step two. Show increased output.",
    "uid": "304629909d8d259a",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 685.37,
    "end": 689.37
  },
  {
    "text": "Call in sick and the work off-site for a day or two.",
    "uid": "69e017d12c36251d",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 690.37,
    "end": 693.37
  },
  {
    "text": "Make this period ultra productive.",
    "uid": "9254b43f01d1f461",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 694.37,
    "end": 696.37
  },
  {
    "text": "Step three. Quantify company benefits.",
    "uid": "f539c65bccd36d46",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 698.81,
    "end": 700.81
  },
  {
    "text": "Showcase just how productive you've been during these days. Two your boss.",
    "uid": "9cc8b65206e651b0",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 701.81,
    "end": 705.81
  },
  {
    "text": "Emphasize the company benefits that this has. Step four.",
    "uid": "92899091c46d6708",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 706.81,
    "end": 712.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Suggest a revocable trial.",
    "uid": "20f3c999b0260e62",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 713.12,
    "end": 715.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Ask the boss for a vocable trial of working remote for two weeks, two days per week.",
    "uid": "0677961c9b90fdf3",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 716.12,
    "end": 721.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Your fallback plan is one day per week if this request is denied.",
    "uid": "5668137ba065956b",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 722.12,
    "end": 725.12
  },
  {
    "text": "Again, make these days the most productive ever.",
    "uid": "37b7077fcf7302a8",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 726.12,
    "end": 731.37
  },
  {
    "text": "Step five. Expand time spent remotely.",
    "uid": "67bb778a8190aead",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 732.37,
    "end": 735.37
  },
  {
    "text": "After a successful trial, gradually increase time spent outside the office in additional trial periods until you don't have to be in the office at all.",
    "uid": "f1c693082cdf2452",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 736.37,
    "end": 744.37
  },
  {
    "text": "And that's it for Tim Ferriss for our work week.",
    "uid": "124d0ee38f3598e8",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 749.32,
    "end": 752.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's repeat the key takeaways again.",
    "uid": "42553b5c3b1bd2b4",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 753.32,
    "end": 754.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Joining the new rich is a four step process with the abbreviation deal.",
    "uid": "a713df70dd18b1a5",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 755.32,
    "end": 760.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Relative income beats absolute income. Once you have enough cash flow to support your dreams.",
    "uid": "b59907d666da9bfd",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 761.32,
    "end": 766.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Be more productive by prioritizing tasks and setting short deadlines. Remember Pareto's and Parkinson's law.",
    "uid": "d14934660700c1c2",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 767.32,
    "end": 774.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Out source tasks to multiply yourself and become the ghost in the machine.",
    "uid": "acfb79cf8cccbefd",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 775.32,
    "end": 779.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Meatballs taste better in Sweden.",
    "uid": "a597491780d102c8",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 780.32,
    "end": 783.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Create unrestricted mobility for yourself so that you can experience everything that the world has to offer.",
    "uid": "8338497a43f2085c",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 784.32,
    "end": 789.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Are you able to fill in the blanks? Please comment down below with your answers.",
    "uid": "585fe44d3389ce13",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 792.11,
    "end": 796.11
  },
  {
    "text": "As always, if you're interested in getting the full read of the book, you can support this channel by getting it from the Amazon link in the description.",
    "uid": "5295e19661b4b511",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 796.11,
    "end": 805.42
  },
  {
    "text": "Also, I've been talking a lot about a few money in this video.",
    "uid": "f28850e6b206e4ea",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 806.42,
    "end": 809.42
  },
  {
    "text": "If you're interested in getting inspiration for a lavish lifestyle and hearing about the seven secrets for internet riches, head over to my summary of Dan Lok's book. Now.",
    "uid": "4a6231ebaf5f1ce5",
    "source": "The_Swedish_Investor - THE_4-HOUR_WORK_WEEK_BY_TIM_FERRISS",
    "start": 810.42,
    "end": 819.42
  }
]